WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.800
This is a map of our school.

00:03.480 --> 00:06.920
There are six buildings in our school.

00:07.440 --> 00:10.920
A library, an office building,

00:11.200 --> 00:13.200
a classroom building,

00:13.560 --> 00:15.400
a dining hall,

00:15.760 --> 00:17.560
a sports hall,

00:17.880 --> 00:20.080
and a science building.

00:21.200 --> 00:23.360
In the middle of the school,

00:23.560 --> 00:26.000
is a big playground.

00:27.000 --> 00:34.000
The library is on the left of the playground near the school gate.

00:34.400 --> 00:39.400
There are many books, maps, and computers in it.

00:40.200 --> 00:46.400
Behind the library, on the left, are the school offices.

00:47.400 --> 00:51.600
Between this building and the dining hall,

00:52.000 --> 00:57.000
is the classroom building with 24 classrooms.

00:58.000 --> 01:03.000
On the right of the classroom building is the dining hall.

01:04.200 --> 01:09.200
In front of the dining hall is the sports hall.

01:09.800 --> 01:14.600
And the building in front of that is for science.

01:15.400 --> 01:21.400
There are six science labs and five computer rooms in the science building.

01:21.600 --> 01:27.000
And the building in front of that is for science.

